Class ControllerJson

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vangav.backend.play_framework.controllers_generator.json.ControllerJson

  • public class ControllerJson
extends java.lang.Object
    ControllerJson is the json representation of a controller

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      boolean is_preset
      is_preset is true if this controller is a preset and false otherwise preset controllers provide known functionalities (e.g.: Facebook login, Google login, etc ...)
      java.lang.String name
      name represents the controller's name (e.g.: Login, Comment, Tweet, etc ...)
      RequestParamJson[] request_params
      request_params represents the controller's request params
      ResponseParamJson[] response_params
      response_params represents the controller's response params for a JSON type response
      java.lang.String response_type
      response_type represents the controller's response type (JSON, FILE or HTML)
      java.lang.String type
      type represents the controller's type (GET or POST)
